  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A jagged shard of what was once a great arcane staff. The crackling energies contained within have not faded despite the staff's ruin. Requires attunement by a sorcerer, warlock, or wizard.</p><p>While attuned, you gain a +2 bonus to spell attack rolls and you regain 1d6+2 expended charges at dawn (maximum 50).</p><p><strong>Crackling Surge.</strong> When you make a ranged spell attack, you can channel the shard's energy. On a hit, the attack deals an additional 1d10 force damage.</p><p><strong>Arcane Overload (15 charges).</strong> As an action, expend 15 charges. Each creature in a 20-foot-radius sphere centred on you must make a DC 16 Constitution saving throw, taking 8d6 force damage on a failure or half on a success.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
